- Tidak.

457
00:28:10,049 --> 00:28:11,082
Oh Tuhan,

458
00:28:11,107 --> 00:28:13,763
kita tidak patut tonton
"Roman Holiday".

459
00:28:14,113 --> 00:28:15,247
Datang sini.

460
00:28:15,513 --> 00:28:17,329
- Cepat.
- Baiklah.

461
00:28:28,314 --> 00:28:29,314
Lihat ini.

462
00:28:29,339 --> 00:28:31,809
