597
00:36:34,122 --> 00:36:35,722
Bagaimana keadaan hari ini?

598
00:36:35,747 --> 00:36:38,347
Ada sesiapa yang hendap awak...

599
00:36:38,372 --> 00:36:40,172
atau mengikuti awak?

600
00:36:44,721 --> 00:36:46,121
Maafkan saya.

601
00:36:48,251 --> 00:36:49,851
Siapa awak...

602
00:36:49,876 --> 00:36:51,676
dan kenapa awak ekori saya?

603
00:36:52,570 --> 00:36:56,870
- Begini, pen awak...
- Awak peminat?

604
00:36:57,716 --> 00:37:00,316
Awak tersilap, tuan.
Saya bukan selebriti.

605
00:37:00,341 --> 00:37:03,141
Saya hanya gadis biasa
yang sangat cantik.

606
00:37:10,383 --> 00:37:11,883
Tunggu sebentar.

607
00:37:13,177 --> 00:37:14,677
Kenapa awak terus mengikuti saya?

608
00:37:14,702 --> 00:37:17,002
